Package org.spongepowered.api.event.world

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChunkEvent
    Describes events which involve a Chunk.
    ChunkForcedEvent  
    ChunkLoadEvent
    Called when a Chunk is loaded in an existing World map
    ChunkPostGenerateEvent
    Called when a Chunk has just been generated.
    ChunkPostPopulateEvent
    Called when a Chunk has just been populated.
    ChunkPreGenerateEvent
    Called when a Chunk is about to be generated.
    ChunkPrePopulateEvent
    Called when a Chunk is about to be populated.
    ChunkUnforcedEvent  
    ChunkUnloadEvent
    Called when a Chunk is unloaded.
    GameRuleChangeEvent
    Called when a GameRule is changed.
    WorldEvent
    Represents an event that pertains to a World.
    WorldLoadEvent
    Called when a Game loads a World level.
    WorldUnloadEvent
    Called when a Game unloads a World level.
